 Peter Bakota,
 Boris Ivic and
 Tibor Csonkas.

  Here we put some thoughts before you continue reading further ( no
 special order or theme ).

 PETER BAKOTA :
  I hope you like this game. But if you find any bug or you want to tell
 your suggestions please contact with TENAX Software at this address :

                   Peter Bakota
                   TENAX SOFTWARE
                   Sabo Miklosa 21
                   24000 Subotica
                   Yugoslavia

 Or call the number 024-32-289.

 BORIS IVIC :

  This life is a boring one, so let's make a littile more interesting ! Of
 course, usually it ends up in war or some other kind of stupid behaviour.
 I hope this game will at least, by one small part of that stupidity,
 remove wars from reality as we know it, and put it on computer screen(s)
 once and for all ! That's all from me. Bye !

 TIBOR CSONKAS :
  Hm, hm..., Bye.


